                    "stepText": "Great, with the correct formulas identified, now substitute the expression for $!$GM$!$ (from the gravitational field strength) into the escape speed formula. This will simplify the expression under the square root to $!$2gr$!$. Calculate the numerical value of $!$2 \\times g \\times r$!$ using $!$g = 1.8 \\text{ N/kg}$!$ and $!$r = 1.5 \\times 10^6 \\text{ m}$!$.",
